reviews.text: If you're looking for a chill place with a great ambience then this is it. Service isn't the best but the ambience and vibe makes up for it. The ginger lemon tea goes really well with any hookah. The desserts didn't disappoint also.

Definitely one of the best hookah places I've been to! Very friendly and social environment and the hookah here is so much smoother and tastes so good! Everything was truly amazing! GREAT service! Kelly really cared about our satisfaction and made us feel welcome. Will definitely come again!

Best hookah lounge in dfw by far. Super clean  awesome atmosphere and mood setting. The ladies do an amazing job on the hookah and go above and beyond to make sure the hookahs have no complaint. Their mint lemonade is a smoothie item but is awesome. For me, no hookah is complete without a mint lemonade frozen drink. I love the ambiance. I also love the fact that that owner came to us asking how our experience was and wanted feedback. An extremely kind guy.

This is my new goto place for hookah now.
